Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:39.07,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,STAND UP まだ僕を呼んでる声が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:44.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,「YES」だって「NO」だって 関係はないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:49.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,STARDUST 穴だらけのゲームスコア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:54.71,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,DEAD OR LIE DEAD OR LIE　自由を見たくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:59.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,GO OUT 閉ざされた夜に I'll be eaten away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:04.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,透明な武器を手に入れてる LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:09.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんの為に　何を守る　長い待ちは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:14.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぶち壞すこの彈丸で！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:19.74,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER LIE モノクロな光のない世界でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:24.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER END NEVER LIE　心は染まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:30.50,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,THE END OF WORLD　絕望に僅かな希望握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:39.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,震える指で狙い定めて 未來を探せ！
Comment: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:34.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————OPCN——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:39.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,STAND UP 呼喚我的聲音未絕於耳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:44.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無論答案是「YES」或「NO」 都沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:49.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,STARDUST 遊戲結果已滿是漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:54.71,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,DEAD OR LIE DEAD OR LIE 希冀能看到自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:59.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,GO OUT 在這憋悶的夜晚 我終將被腐蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:04.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無形的武器已然到手 LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:09.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了什麼 要守護什麼 才經過漫長等待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:14.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就用這顆子彈破壞一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:19.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER LIE 即使在這僅剩黑白 暗無光輝的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:24.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER END NEVER LIE 心靈絕不沾染黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:30.50,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,THE END OF WORLD 在絕望中握住僅存的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:39.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,用顫抖的手指瞄準目標 去追尋未來！
Comment: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:25.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDJP——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:35.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終わりが始まるアリアと共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:40.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白旗を掲げた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:46.09,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脱獄の果てに歓声の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:50.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手錠突き付けられ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:56.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ほら、見て　愚かな駒よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:23:01.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}断罪の茶番
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:03.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}独壇場Funky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:06.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その目で見ろ　競争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:11.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}Forget
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:11.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:14.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多発的な展開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:17.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人の波を掻き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:19.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫べ　My Justice，Right Way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:22.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Make it a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:24.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感心できるのはFunky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:27.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喪失だけが拒止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:32.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}導いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:35.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:37.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.56,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:41.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:43.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No, we're already over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:45.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody loves despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:48.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I'll sadly go from the end
Comment: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:25.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDCN——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:35.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴隨著結尾即開始的詠嘆調
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:40.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高舉白旗的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:46.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃獄後的歡呼聲中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:50.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被强行拷上了手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:56.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:23:01.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這定罪的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:03.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇異的獨角戲舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:06.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看著 競争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:11.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遺落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:11.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺騙吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:14.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多線並行的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:17.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撥開人群
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:19.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊著 這是我正義的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:22.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:24.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得讚美的驚恐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:27.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯獨拒绝喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:32.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:35.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過於艷麗的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:37.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帶有偏見的分類
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:41.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:43.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我們已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:45.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都愛著绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:48.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會滿懷悲傷地離去
